        public java.lang.Integer getDropDownMapFieldKey(java.lang.Integer fieldID)
        The field key for getting the corresponding map from dropdown container. The SystemSelects and the Pickers are stored under the same key in the container (the key of the SystemSelect field) (for ex. manager, responsible, originator, changedBy and user picker share the same person map) The CustomSelects are stored under their own fieldIDs
